.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, january, december, february, april
5 different games are played: monopoly, poker, chess, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, parkour, swimming, rowing, golf
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, cooking, baking, collecting
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in march
2. the person playing poker is the owner of the dog
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's birthday is in january
4. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing
5. the person who's birthday is in january is to the right of the person who's birthday is in december
6. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the snails
7. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's birthday is in february
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who's sport is parkour is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is baking
13. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is golf
14. the person playing mah-jongg is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Game	|   mah-jongg	|    chess	|     monopoly	|    poker	|    backgammon	|
| Birthday		|    february	|      april	|      march	|     december	|     january	|
| Hobby	|     collecting	|      rock-climbing	|      cooking	| baking	|     writing	|
| Sport		|     parkour	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| rowing	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
